Mark Shields and New York
Times columnist David Brooks.

00:06.633 --> 00:07.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Welcome, gentlemen.

00:07.633 --> 00:09.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So, Mark, welcome back.

00:09.100 --> 00:10.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: Thank you, Judy.

00:10.300 --> 00:12.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We
missed you last week.

00:12.566 --> 00:14.600 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
The Donald Trump Jr. story.

00:14.600 --> 00:19.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
