04:58.666 --> 04:59.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MARK SHIELDS: Mm-hmm.

04:59.666 --> 05:00.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
No, it is, Judy.

05:00.700 --> 05:02.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
