the United States intelligence
agencies and professionals by

05:12.300 --> 05:16.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
President Trump, candidate Trump
and now President Trump, whether
Russia -- you know, I can't

05:16.733 --> 05:18.033 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
