05:18.033 --> 05:20.066 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Yes, probably, but not for sure.

05:20.066 --> 05:25.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I mean, here they are, the Trump
Tower with the people, their
names approved on the visitors

05:27.000 --> 05:31.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
list for the meeting in the
Trump Tower, and pretending
they didn't know it.

05:33.000 --> 05:35.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, no, it's -- David is right.

05:35.366 --> 05:40.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
In a management sense, it's
just been incredible, Judy.

05:42.466 --> 05:45.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Apparently, it's hit the
president or someone has
gotten to the president,
because his statement

05:45.566 --> 05:50.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
