06:05.433 --> 06:08.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: It does open
up a bunch of questions,
like what were the -- this
-- as the intelligence

06:08.300 --> 06:12.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
